       Welcome!
         
           
             
               
              
               
             
             
               
        
        The RLGA is a nonprofit
    organization founded in 1989. 
     
    Our members are women of all skill levels who enjoy the game of golf and, above all, want to have fun!  
     
    The RLGA offers regular weekday (Wednesday) and weekend (Saturday and
    Sunday) morning tee times as well as bi-weekly competitions and monthly
    tournaments. 
     
    Whether you are a casual player or a seasoned pro, the RLGA has
        something for you! 
     
 For further information about our club, please visit our
    Membership Info link. 
         
         
        
         
           
             
                
             
